{"tid":1784663,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"學校內投票風氣","createTime":"2019-12-15T23:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T15:17:49.000Z","uid":162008,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f47c963e035240243e72f4b29046058f2082ed48","tid":1784663,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T23:07:47.000Z","msg":"老一輩黎講，以前無咩野可以投票，唔興投票，亦唔知道投票既意義。<br />\n<br />\n而後生年青既，中小學除左學生會選舉，接觸投票既機會亦唔多<br />\n<br />\n所以我整左個App, 希望培養大家投票既習慣同風氣，只要大家知道自己果票有幾重要，買票，種票既成本就會大大提升。<br />\n<br />\n亦變相令每一屆既區選唔再可以係咁容易可以連任，從而逼出區議員為民請命，為社區做實事既動力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以好希望大家可以幫手將呢個app 宣傳俾自己家人朋友，發放出去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 香港地區專屬的投票平台<br />\n<br />\nIOS 版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/香港地投票-hkvote/id1485087934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%B0%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8-hkvote%2Fid1485087934&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=d3621d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/香港地投票-hkvote/id1485087934</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid 版<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Muisco.HKVote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.Muisco.HKVote&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hvUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=3179f302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Muisco.HKVote</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"efc8af0d90925bab064d8b245f85b8c9eb1fc773","tid":1784663,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d2efff55547f1419b3ca9eb072385cbd034ad0a","tid":1784663,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85cb9f79d00d104634654a785e91a42f